{"tid":2110033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★科技創新大賽獲獎作品疑抄襲　市科協：研究角度不同","createTime":"2020-07-15T15:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T15:12:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12ee11d6128de55491b2a2b9e42d9b47a8ec027b","tid":2110033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"全國青少年科技創新大賽三甲作品先後被質疑造假。其中高中組2018年一項一等獎作品被指與陸軍軍醫大學2018年的一篇碩士論文部分內容重複。重慶市科學技術協會科技服務中心稱，兩篇論文的研究角度不同。賽事主辦單位已着手調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200715/bkn-20200715043404614-0715_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200715%2Fbkn-20200715043404614-0715_00952_001.html&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n36GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=a444cbf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200715/bkn-20200715043404614-0715_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"285648bc982d70a2b5c85bda351a58e4a91f62ca","tid":2110033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad2f15da84cfbf40242a1c526c7e9e5443571e2","tid":2110033,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.intelligenthq.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/photocopier-machine-330x220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.intelligenthq.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Fphotocopier-machine-330x220.jpg&h=cd3af859&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"419af83234a116a533e475fef5484b49c183b601","tid":2110033,"uid":53026,"like